      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_841D3FC0-221F-0135-6ECE-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-create-hyperlinks-to-user-or-group-files-in-the-Rich/ta-p/324" target="_blank">add links to group or user files</a>. The name of the page will appear in the Rich Content Editor and flash yellow. Then the name will turn blue, indicating it is a link. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
